{"tid":1418112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喂醒未呀？咪撚再睇分化post","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:48:55.000Z","uid":263905,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"852a0ff4b04269f31b6889f1cecd1bafaf0d7185","tid":1418112,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"呢一個禮拜恆指跌左2000點呀<br />\n就快跌至全年低位<br />\n<br />\n呢一星期發生左咩事？<br />\n除左個個禮拜六日都上演既街頭勇武抗爭<br />\n就係只係宣傳左一個星期多少少既<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.5罷工</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我一早講撚左<br />\n只要你有組織有宣傳咁去罷工<br />\n未罷啲仆街已經驚到瀨尿<br />\n之前工聯會講明叫人唔好罷工<br />\n各大公司警告員工罷工會搞你<br />\n就係因為驚<br />\n<br />\n股市係信心遊戲<br />\n你睇呢一星期條恆指走勢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆街過山車咁衝落去</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n到左8.5<br />\n一開市又跌500幾點<br />\n政府個記招<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對罷工隻字不提</span></strong></span><br />\n連陳健波講經濟<br />\n都唔敢提推送中條例之後嘅跌市<br />\n淨係夠膽講第一二季啲舊嘢<br />\n<br />\n以政府一貫做法<br />\n仲唔將啲小事化大係咁講咩<br />\n唯一解釋就係因為對佢哋真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好大影響</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢最想就係你班友<br />\n日日夜夜同啲狗打游擊<br />\n周圍放火周圍搞事<br />\n仲有一次真係搞着啲街坊<br />\n就雨傘2.0<br />\n<br />\n醒未？"},{"pid":"a596d6747fb73e96d727f7d20ac6f1300112b6a3","tid":1418112,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af9a04c560609aec8e136ec4b5edda4a73bbb0bb","tid":1418112,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"505223f6fc260e49c547389adf78e10cc52de127","tid":1418112,"uid":101057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1bb7df35e4b09d5aebe3f00943822bda1b7880a","tid":1418112,"uid":263905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:5